  entryId: day_03_bridge_repaired
  dayNumber: 3
  title: The Bridge Was Repaired
  bodyText: 'They do not remember who built the bridge.

    But this morning, people
    crossed the river for the first time.


    The market is louder now.

    Someone
    brought tools from outside the village.'
